# Active Services Environment Configuration Example

Copy values into each service-specific .env file as needed.

## Frontend Origins (used by API gateway CORS)
```
FRONTEND_CHATBOT_ORIGIN=http://localhost:3000
FRONTEND_DASHBOARD_ORIGIN=http://localhost:3001
```

## API Gateway (service:5000)
```
APP_ENV=development
LOG_LEVEL=INFO
GATEWAY_HOST=localhost
GATEWAY_PORT=5000
RATE_LIMIT_DEFAULT=120 per minute
DATABASE_SERVICE_URL=http://localhost:5004
REALTIME_VOICE_SERVICE_URL=http://localhost:5005
REALTIME_VOICE_SERVICE_WS_URL=ws://localhost:5005/ws/realtime-voice
```

## Database Manager (service:5004)
```
APP_ENV=development
LOG_LEVEL=INFO
SERVICE_HOST=localhost
SERVICE_PORT=5004
SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-id.supabase.co
SUPABASE_KEY=sb_secret_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
DB_HOST=db.xxxxx.supabase.co
DB_PORT=5432
DB_USER=postgres
DB_PASSWORD=your_password_here
DB_NAME=postgres
COLLECTION_NAME=course_materials_vectors
API_GATEWAY_ORIGIN=http://localhost:5000
RATE_LIMIT_DEFAULT=120 per minute
```

## Realtime Voice Service (service:5005)
```
APP_ENV=development
LOG_LEVEL=INFO
SERVICE_HOST=localhost
SERVICE_PORT=5005
API_GATEWAY_ORIGIN=http://localhost:5000
DATABASE_MANAGER_URL=http://localhost:5004
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here
OPENAI_REALTIME_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini-realtime-preview
OPENAI_REALTIME_TRANSCRIPTION_MODEL=whisper-1
OPENAI_REALTIME_VOICE=alloy
OPENAI_REALTIME_USE_EPHEMERAL_TOKEN=false
RATE_LIMIT_DEFAULT=120 per minute
```

## Notes
- Active backend path policy for frontends is /api/query/* through API gateway.
- Keep real secrets only in local .env files, never in source files.
